<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mn">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Данс Идэвхжүүлэлт</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          Roboto, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f7ff;
        color: #1a1f36;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 30px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 650px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 50px;
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      h1 {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #6366f1);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        font-size: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }
      p {
        margin: 18px 0;
        font-size: 17px;
        color: #4a5568;
      }
      .code {
        display: block;
        width: fit-content;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 20px 40px;
        font-size: 28px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #6366f1);
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }
      .code:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.35);
      }
      .signature {
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 30px;
        border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 45px;
        padding-top: 25px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 15px;
        border-top: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
      }
      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      .logo img {
        max-width: 180px;
        height: auto;
      }
      strong {
        color: #1e293b;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .highlight {
        background: linear-gradient(
          120deg,
          rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1) 0%,
          rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1) 100%
        );
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <!-- Add your company logo here -->
        <!-- <img src="logo.png" alt="Company Logo"> -->
      </div>
      <h1>Баталгаажуулах код</h1>
      <p>Сайн байна уу, <strong class="highlight"><%= name %></strong>!</p>
      <p>
        Бүртгүүлсэнд баярлалаа. Та доорх идэвхжүүлэлтийн кодыг ашиглан өөрийн
        бүртгэлийг идэвхжүүлнэ үү:
      </p>
      <div class="code"><%= activationCode %></div>
      <div class="signature">
        <p>Хүндэтгэсэн,</p>
        <p><strong>Танай Компани</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Манай Компани. Бүх эрх хуулиар
          хамгаалагдсан.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
